org.springframework.boot.autoconfigure.jmx

Class JmxAutoConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.springframework.boot.autoconfigure.jmx.JmxAutoConfiguration
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Aware, BeanFactoryAware, EnvironmentAware

    @Configuration
 @ConditionalOnClass(value=org.springframework.jmx.export.MBeanExporter.class)
 @ConditionalOnProperty(prefix="spring.jmx",
                       name="enabled",
                       havingValue="true",
                       matchIfMissing=true)
public class JmxAutoConfiguration
extends Object
implements EnvironmentAware, BeanFactoryAware
    Auto-configuration to enable/disable Spring's EnableMBeanExport mechanism based on configuration properties.

    To disable auto export of annotation beans set spring.jmx.enabled: false.

    Author:
    Christian Dupuis, Madhura Bhave, Artsiom Yudovin
